The median seta between the two strong terminal telsonic setae is very short in the new species and in P. mediosetosus from the Cape Basin (
Mühlenhardt-Siegel, 2014
) but only little shorter than the lateral setae in the female from the Weddell Sea, while equal in length to the lateral setae in males from the Weddell Sea and Brazil Basin.
